        </div>
        <div class="flex-auto">
          <h5 class="h3 mt0 mb1 regular dark-blue">Nathan Manousos</h5>
          <h5 class="h4 mt0 mb1 med-gray regular">
              Founder, 
              <a target="_blank" href="http://flinto.com">Flinto</a>
          </h5>
          <p class="med-gray">I'm an independent developer, designer and juggler who is nuts about great products. I'm the founder of <a href="https://www.flinto.com/" target="_blank">Flinto</a>, creator of <a href="https://www.imagesnap.com/" target="_blank">ImageSnap</a> and an instructor at <a href="http://ga.co/" target="_blank">General Assembly</a>. Previously I was the designer of <a href="http://www.echofon.com/" target="_blank">Echofon</a> and a UI developer at <a href="http://www.blurb.com/" target="_blank">Blurb</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>


